messages.message:
Mind blowing engagement from ~1500 students and 100+ faculty at LPU. 
• students built apps and conversed with their documents on stage as part of workshop 
• We’re creating a community of 20 most interested students and faculty to become our ambassadors on the campus. 
• Sharing API access with ~10 student developers who have ideas / use cases for integration. 
Kudos to @Ab @avi and @vivek.prakash for figuring so many things on the fly and making this weekend a massive success. We will share a more detailed update on Monday.
